"What on earth is this...?!"

When I returned to my home on the way back to the village, what greeted me was, in a word, a devastating scene.

When was the last time you went back?

I don't remember every detail too well, but I would never have left the place in such a mess.

All the doors were opened and everything I hadn't taken to the hut was spilled on the floor.

At first glance, several things were missing, including some furniture that had probably been smashed for fun.

Perhaps it was anger or fear, but something cold welled up from deep within my bones and my hands began to tremble.

This...was it a burglar?!

